text: South Karelia () is a part of Karelia and a region in Finland. Neighbouring regions are Kymenlaakso, Southern Savonia, and North Karelia. Transportation: Freight trains from Russia are coming (as of 2024) thru the border village Vainikkala.https://yle.fi/a/74-20106170.
